cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper is about a neural topic model for reviews, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves neural networks and deep learning, which are common in the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques, which are common in the sub-category cs.IR. Additionally, the paper involves aspects of artificial intelligence (AI) and computer vision (CV), which are common in the sub-categories cs.AI and cs.CV, respectively.
